CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 30, 1966, pg. 2B reads: "Mr. And Mrs. Herbert Bryant Jr........Cutting Cake (Harris photo)." Portion of accompanying article reads: "Brown-Bryandt Wedding Held At St. Richards - The recent weddign of Miss Victoria Janice Brown of Pittsburgh adn Herbert L. Bryant Jr. of Washington, D.C. and Albany, N.Y. was marked by beauty and solemnity..."
TitMainTitle: Groom Leon Bryan Jr. and bride Victoria Janice Brown Bryan cutting three tiered wedding cake in the Greene Hearth
